```plantuml
@startuml victorshinya_serverless-chatbot

actor User
participant "IBM Cloud Functions" as CloudFunctions
participant "Watson Assistant" as Watson
participant "MongoDB" as MongoDB

User -> CloudFunctions: Send Message
activate CloudFunctions

CloudFunctions -> Watson: Invoke assistant.js
activate Watson
Watson -> Watson: Process NLP\n(intent recognition, entity extraction)
Watson -> CloudFunctions: Return Response
deactivate Watson

CloudFunctions -> MongoDB: Invoke mongodb.js\n(Store Conversation)
activate MongoDB
MongoDB -> CloudFunctions: Acknowledge Storage
deactivate MongoDB

CloudFunctions -> User: Return Chatbot Response
deactivate CloudFunctions

@enduml
```